1
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:32,960
Mr. Yamamoto.

2
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,960
Lord Ito has finished his meal.

3
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,690
He is waiting for you upstairs.

4
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,210
There's one more thing.

5
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,880
Hu Wenyi has sent you a gift.

6
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:45,940
Bring it in.

7
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,880
Behave.

8
00:01:58,520 --> 00:02:00,080
Excellent.

9
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,360
Pretty girl.

10
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,760
Hehehe.

11
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,360
This is the new head of our Hu family,

12
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,800
Miss Hu Linglong.

13
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,720
So,

14
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,960
you are the

15
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,920
new head of the Hu family.

16
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,240
What we saw in the account books is correct.

17
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,560
British merchants have indeed been forcing the tea prices down.

18
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,760
The British merchants are powerful.

19
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,220
We must endure it if we can.

20
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,079
Long'er.

21
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,400
Auntie.

22
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,720
Zhinian,

23
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:39,000
you came just in time.

24
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,880
I heard the British merchants are causing trouble in the tea garden.

25
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,400
I was worried, so I came to check.

26
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,520
Linglong isn't here.

27
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,040
She should be in the tea garden.

28
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,440
Auntie,

29
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,100
wait here. I'll go take a look.

30
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,360
Slow down.

31
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,300
I am the newly appointed head.

32
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,620
I heard this has happened many times,

33
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,680
but I don't know the details.

34
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,680
If you still want to buy our tea,

35
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:02,320
let's go to the tea house to talk.

36
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,640
Uncle Zhao,

37
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,000
go call the tea farmers.

38
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,920
I'm setting a new rule today.

39
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,120
From now on, if tea farmers have trouble,

40
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,320
they can come directly to me.

41
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,250
Do not stop them.

42
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,280
Also,

43
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,040
bring the account books.

44
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,960
Yes, Miss.

45
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:39,200
Miss,

46
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,730
here are the account books.

47
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,840
Mr. Charles.

48
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,480
You've always bought

49
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:52,010
our finished tea products.

50
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,960
Now you want raw leaves,

51
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,520
and we agree to that.

52
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,600
But

53
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,040
you keep forcing prices down.

54
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,770
They really can't go any lower.

55
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,720
The English firm plans to

56
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,440
sign a new agreement with the Hu family.

57
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,560
I will lower the purchase price of tea

58
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,000
by another 30 percent.

59
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,600
Otherwise,

60
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:13,480
watch your tea rot in the warehouse.

61
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:17,440
Why are you still holding back?

62
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,079
He's right.

63
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,240
The Hu family's business

64
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,040
really relies on these British merchants.

65
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,360
For the Hu family,

66
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,520
I have to endure it.

67
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,840
Mr. Charles,

68
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,300
please show some respect.

69
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,240
You can't insult people like this.

70
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,300
What are the people in the back doing?

71
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,360
Go beat him up.

72
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,960
This is so frustrating.

73
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:41,640
If you won't,

74
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,440
I'll help you.

75
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:50,920
I...

76
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,720
Why am I back again?

77
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,480
Watch me teach you a lesson.

78
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,520
Don't act on impulse.

79
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,760
I just took over as the head of the family.

80
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,560
I can't ruin the Hu family's business

81
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,220
for a moment of satisfaction.

82
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,080
You are not welcome in the Hu family tea garden.

83
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:17,120
Get out of here right now.

84
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,200
How dare you.

85
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,540
Did you hear me?

86
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,040
Hey!

87
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,300
How dare you hit me!

88
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,120
I belong to the British firm!

89
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:27,440
Your East India Company

90
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,360
commits atrocities,

91
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,840
burning, killing and looting all over the world.

92
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,160
How many innocent people have you killed?

93
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,440
Have you ever counted?

94
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,600
Now you come to

95
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,600
the Chinese land to do evil,

96
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,080
dumping opium and plundering by force,

97
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,360
ruining our tea and harming our people!

98
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,040
Well said!

99
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,240
No.

100
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,800
Shut up.

101
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,000
The Hu family can't afford to offend

102
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,320
these British merchants.

103
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,480
Did you hear me?

104
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,400
Ah!

105
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,440
You are asking for death!

106
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,520
Stop!

107
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,560
This is the Hu family's tea garden.

108
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,420
Let me see who dares to make a move.

109
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,200
Zhinian.

110
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,200
Didn't he ignore me?

111
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,260
Why at this time...

112
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,600
You!

113
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,960
Just you wait.

114
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,130
Are you okay?

115
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:14,840
Linglong.

116
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,440
No.

117
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,320
Linglong.

118
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:18,800
Linglong!

119
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,360
Miss, watch out!

120
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,560
Miss.

121
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:23,520
Miss.

122
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,040
Strange.

123
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,040
How could she come back

124
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,360
so fast this time?

125
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:34,560
Linglong.

126
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,840
Miss.

127
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,240
Slow down.

128
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,960
We will compensate you

129
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,600
for the tea leaves damaged today.

130
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,480
Miss,

131
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,000
since you protect us like this,

132
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,560
we must support you.

133
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,480
Support you.

134
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,880
Thank you for your trust.

135
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:55,740
Uncle Zhao,

136
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,159
please see everyone out.

137
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:57,490
Okay.

138
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,159
Everyone.

139
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,400
Follow me.

140
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,520
Come.

141
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,040
This way.

142
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,640
Thank you, Miss. We are leaving.

143
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:12,600
Zhinian.

144
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,960
Thank you

145
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,860
for saving me again today.

146
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:16,680
Linglong,

147
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,740
no need to thank me.

148
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,650
Zhinian. Linglong.

149
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,200
You.

150
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,120
You go first.

151
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,200
Linglong.

152
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,480
You go first.

153
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,960
Zhinian.

154
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:34,159
Actually, what I said in the ancestral hall

155
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,760
was not my intention.

156
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:39,880
Linglong.

157
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,490
Then why didn't you tell me?

158
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,520
Zhinian.

159
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,800
It's not that I don't want to say,

160
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,040
but even if I did,

161
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,520
you wouldn't believe it.

162
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,520
Zhinian,

163
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,300
what do you want to tell me?

164
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,440
Yesterday in the ancestral hall,

165
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,400
I said I passed

166
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,200
the naval commander selection.

167
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,130
Do you remember?

168
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,440
Now I'm waiting for

169
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,000
the letter of appointment.

170
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,160
I don't know when I'll have to leave.

171
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:15,880
Once I leave,

172
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,580
I don't know when I'll be back.

173
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,200
Zhinian.

174
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,880
If you receive the letter,

175
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,610
can you come find me right away?

176
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,240
I have something to tell you.

177
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,460
What do you want to tell me?

178
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,880
You'll know when the time comes.

179
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,520
Promise me first.

180
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,159
Okay,

181
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,640
I promise you.

182
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,080
Miss,

183
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,409
Madam is here to see you.

184
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,530
Zhinian,

185
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,640
I'll go first.

186
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,360
I've already paid.

187
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,160
Get out.

188
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:12,760
Yes,

189
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,640
they are not leaving us any way out.

190
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,560
I want to reduce the tea purchasing price

191
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,960
by another 30%.

192
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,480
You,

193
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,680
just you wait.

194
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,050
Hu Linglong.

195
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,880
I haven't resolved the British merchant's issue yet,

196
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:41,640
what trouble are you making for me again?

197
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,520
No,

198
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,500
I'm here to tell you good news.

199
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,720
I think I found

200
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,250
the way for us to swap souls.

201
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,680
You mean,

202
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:59,160
as long as your emotions fluctuate,

203
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,730
your soul will forcefully occupy my body?

204
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,480
Yes.

205
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,080
Not only that,

206
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:06,080
if both of us agree,

207
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,600
we can also swap souls.

208
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,840
Think about it carefully,

209
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,440
when we swapped souls before,

210
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,970
wasn't it always like this?

211
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,400
And,

212
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,060
I thought about it carefully,

213
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,000
regarding the British merchant today,

214
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,120
I did handle it a bit impulsively.

215
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,360
But I promise you,

216
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,320
if I don't have your consent in the future,

217
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:36,120
I will never occupy your body without permission.

218
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,000
Really?

219
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,360
Really.

220
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,160
However,

221
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,480
I still want to ask you,

222
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,880
do you have any unfulfilled wishes?

223
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:48,240
Why do you ask?

224
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,120
That's because

225
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,800
only if I fulfill your wish

226
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,000
can I return

227
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,560
to heaven.

228
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:03,360
Dad, what are you doing?

229
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,200
I'm grinding tea.

230
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,240
Qingyun.

231
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:08,040
All businesses in the world,

232
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,770
none of them remain unchanged.

233
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,920
If the tea doesn't change,

234
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,180
people's hearts will.

235
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,080
It's fine if you don't understand now.

236
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,560
Just remember my words.

237
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,960
As for unfulfilled wishes,

238
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,490
I actually have one.

239
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:24,440
What is it?

240
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,160
I...

241
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,560
want to improve Qimen black tea

242
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,480
and make it flourish.
